  "3199080": {
    "name": "HellPunk: Purgatorium",
    "steam_appid": 3199080,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199080/extras/8af307af2c610ffa64d162a06c2034ce.avif?t=1770368742\" width=1560 height=234 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[We’ve opened an official Discord server! Development updates and direct communication with the developers take place there, so we’d love for you to join us.]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199080/extras/1e57ad3193e2d5bd453c493b661b6a8b.avif?t=1770368742\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199080/extras_big/1e57ad3193e2d5bd453c493b661b6a8b.avif?t=1770368742 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HellPunk-血腥动作Roguelite游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《HellPunk》是一款在蒸汽朋克风格地狱中展开的 Roguelite 血腥暴力动作游戏。 以豪爽的战斗爆杀丑陋的地狱居民，完成充满动作感的任务，到达最终密室吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199080/extras/254b242cc66a595f919adab970e9ec73.avif?t=1770368742\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199080/extras_big/254b242cc66a595f919adab970e9ec73.avif?t=1770368742 width=800 height=524 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事情节</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿什-德雷克（Asher Drake）是一个一生坎坷的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 年前，他唯一的亲人妹妹失踪了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他至今仍在全国各地奔波，试图找到妹妹失踪的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直到有一天，他遭遇了一场意想不到的意外。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当他睁开眼睛时，看到的只有蒸汽、旋转的机器和... 一座塔</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿什意识到，他的哥哥就在眼前这座巨塔中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了找到失踪弟弟的真相，他开始在地狱般的高塔中奋力奔跑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199080/extras/ddeec2db275fc37d1ba123fe74b82bf9.poster.avif?t=1770368742\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199080/extras/ddeec2db275fc37d1ba123fe74b82bf9.webm?t=1770368742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199080/extras/ddeec2db275fc37d1ba123fe74b82bf9.mp4?t=1770368742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >侧滚动平台动作roguelite游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HellPunk是一款roguelike动作平台游戏，每次的地图和敌人构成都不相同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199080/extras/69b754aedd0215d9bc8426fb709c7421.poster.avif?t=1770368742\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199080/extras/69b754aedd0215d9bc8426fb709c7421.webm?t=1770368742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199080/extras/69b754aedd0215d9bc8426fb709c7421.mp4?t=1770368742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >鲜血四溅、血肉横飞的血腥动作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好迎接血腥和怪异的终极体验吧！每杀死一只怪物，您的肢体就会被扯断或炸飞。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在地狱塔的边缘爆破，将怪物炸得血肉横飞、皮开肉绽、血管外露。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199080/extras/fcd1629c34cbc7523e50d139f1f652db.poster.avif?t=1770368742\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199080/extras/fcd1629c34cbc7523e50d139f1f652db.webm?t=1770368742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199080/extras/fcd1629c34cbc7523e50d139f1f652db.mp4?t=1770368742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >时尚动作，实时切换武器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拿起七宗罪主题武器中的两种，尝试征服地狱塔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在各种武器之间切换，结合自己的技能击倒怪物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199080/extras/d3192e2b1bd7f0cc41c18a7701434ed7.avif?t=1770368742\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199080/extras_big/d3192e2b1bd7f0cc41c18a7701434ed7.avif?t=1770368742 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用各种强化装备定制你的装备</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >齿轮 &quot;具有受所罗门七十二魔神启发而设计的各种不同BUFF</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >技能交换 &quot;可根据自己的喜好交换和增强技能</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手术台 &quot;可通过血石永久增强身体机能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用一系列迷人的强化装备来定制您的装备，这些装备与地狱朋克的独特氛围相得益彰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199080/extras/5082aef14b8adc922d61a255854d43f7.avif?t=1770368742\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199080/extras_big/5082aef14b8adc922d61a255854d43f7.avif?t=1770368742 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富多彩的支线故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您将在基地中遇到各种人类 NPC。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个 NPC 都有自己的故事，并会要求您完成各种任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们的要求可以很简单，比如要求您杀死一只怪物，也可以很复杂，比如迫使您做出残酷的选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些任务都是精心设计的，目的是创造一个独特而新颖的地狱。</p>",
